data.description: IMMEDIATE POSSESSION Beautiful!! Open Concept 3 bedrooms plus office, 3 Baths, 2 Car Garage with Full Unfinished Basement (Rough in plumbing for future bath), and Newer Vinyl Fenced Yard.! Main Floor features Kitchen with, Granite counters, New Backsplash, Breakfast Bar, Stainless Steel Appliances, and Ceramic Flooring. Spacious Great Room with Hardwood floors. Updated Main floor laundry and Mudroom. Upstairs features Large Owners Suite with Walk in closet, and its own Bath. 2 Additional Bedrooms, plus office.and GuestBath. Basement can easily be finished with rough in plumbing for future bath and Ejector Pump. 2nd Refrigerator will stay. Water heater 3 years old. 13 Month Hwa home warranty offered. No Homeowners Association fee/No HOA. Close to Schools, Shopping and Expressway. Low Taxes!!
